Titanic train data.

Titanic train data.

titanic_train

Format

Data frame with columns

PassengerId

Passenger ID

Survived

Passenger Survival Indicator

Pclass

Passenger Class

Name

Name

Sex

Sex

Age

Age

SibSp

Number of Siblings/Spouses Aboard

Parch

Number of Parents/Children Aboard

Ticket

Ticket Number

Fare

Passenger Fare

Cabin

Cabin

Embarked

Port of Embarkation

Source

https://www.kaggle.com/c/titanic/data
